marketinginformation: Why waste your time waiting for your pictures, MP3 files, and digital videos when you can have them instantly? These high-quality Mini B USB 2.0 cables are a cost effective way to maximize the performance of your digital camera, MP3 player, PDA, or digital camcorder. With 480 Mbits/sec of reliable data transfer, you'll spend your time viewing and listening to your AV files, not waiting for them to download. These cables use pure digital data transfer for sharper, more natural images and sound at higher speeds.
